name: $fullUrl
desc:
Returns: The Absolute URL for the resource.  The fullUrl SHALL not disagree with the id in the resource. The fullUrl is a version independent reference to the resource. The fullUrl element SHALL have a value except that: 
* fullUrl can be empty on a POST (although it does not need to when specifying a temporary id for reference in the bundle)
* Results from operations might involve resources that are not identified.
